        Aqua Panic! is a puzzle game that'll put your brain to the test over
      more  than  60  levels!  Make  the  best  use  of   the  interactive
      environment, avoiding obstacles and predators to lead  the  fish  to
      freedom! To help you, you can use a  variety of  tools:  -  Missiles
      that can destroy part of the background - Plants that you  can  grow
      to corral the fish  - Harpoons  to get  rid of  the  most  dangerous
      enemies - Ice to freeze the water  and create  new  passageways  And
      lots more!
